Get the spare tire from out of the boot.

21
00:01:36,310 --> 00:01:38,240
Place the spare tire in position

22
00:01:38,240 --> 00:01:45,240
and hand tighten each wheel bolt. Select the
opposite direction you were using earlier

23
00:01:46,400 --> 00:01:52,259
if using the wrench. You may need to lower
your jacking device

24
00:01:52,259 --> 00:01:59,259
